preference.name: QSEARCH_types_to_avoid_processing
preference.preference_description: Specifies item types to avoid while performing a cacheless search. This allows you to restrict the search to object types that have valid matches and avoid unnecessary processing of object types that can never have valid matches. Valid Values: An array of strings representing the object type names as values. The string must contain the type name of at least one valid object type, for example, Architecture.
